Hmm, yes, a bot probably couldn't fly with a pod like that, but then, 
Havoc was swimming, in the water with the pod. The ship was in the 
ocean when it edjected the pod, and Havoc caught it.

::Havoc::

Hearing something sizzle as fireballs hit the water around him, Havoc 
barely dodges an energy blast, the water around him now steaming. He 
pushes on, his proppelers and engines, though desined for air, 
pushing him forward.

"If there are any Alliance members happening to be swimming in the 
ocean," he says, seeing Demolition land near him, grabbing the bot 
with his free hand.
